name: United in Movement Workout 4
description:
9 Min / As Many Reps As Possible

Compete
30-20-10 of:
•Alternating Hang DB C&J
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

Right into…

30-20-10 of:
•Alternating DB Hang Snatches
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

M: 50 lb. dumbbell
F: 35 lb. dumbbell

Move Hard
30-20-10 of:
•R/L Mountain Climbers
(Touching arms)
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

Right into…

30-20-10 of:
•Plank Up Downs
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

Just Move
30-20-10 of:
•R/L Mountain Climbers
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

Right into…

30-20-10 of:
•Plank Up Downs
(knees allowed)
•Butterfly Sit-Ups

Find full workout details and movement standards at https://unitedinmovement.org/workouts/
